      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original factory luster without a single scratch or chip, while the interior remains pristine and free of any wear. Mechanically, the car performs exactly as it did the day it left the showroom, with all systems functioning perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly investment-grade vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standard.",
